#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:2
msgid "Setting up a Python development environment"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:4
msgid ""
"In this example you will build a Python web application using the [Flask]"
"(https://flask.palletsprojects.com) web framework as an exercise. To make "
"the best use of it, you should be familiar with [defining declarative shell "
"environments](declarative-reproducible-envs)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:7
msgid "Create a new file called `myapp.py` and add the following code:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:9
msgid ""
"#!/usr/bin/env python\n"
"\n"
"from flask import Flask\n"
"\n"
"app = Flask(__name__)\n"
"\n"
"@app.route(\"/\")\n"
"def hello():\n"
"    return {\n"
"        \"message\": \"Hello, Nix!\"\n"
"    }\n"
"\n"
"def run():\n"
"    app.run(host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=5000)\n"
"\n"
"if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n"
"    run()"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:29
msgid ""
"This is a simple Flask application which serves a JSON document with the "
"message `\"Hello, Nix!\"`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:31
msgid "Create a new file `shell.nix` to declare the development environment:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:33
msgid ""
"{ pkgs ? import (fetchTarball \"https://github.com/NixOS/nixpkgs/tarball/"
"nixos-23.11\") {} }:\n"
"\n"
"pkgs.mkShellNoCC {\n"
"  packages = with pkgs; [\n"
"    (python3.withPackages (ps: [ ps.flask ]))\n"
"    curl\n"
"    jq\n"
"  ];\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:45
msgid ""
"This describes a shell environment with an instance of `python3` that "
"includes the `flask` package using [`python3.withPackages`](https://nixos."
"org/manual/nixpkgs/stable/#python.withpackages-function). It also contains "
"[`curl`], a utility to perform web requests, and [`jq`], a tool to parse and "
"format JSON documents."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:51
msgid ""
"Both of them are not Python packages. If you went with Python's [virtualenv]"
"(https://virtualenv.pypa.io/en/latest/), it would not be possible to add "
"these utilities to the development environment without additional manual "
"steps."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:54
msgid "Run `nix-shell` to enter the environment you just declared:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:56
msgid ""
"$ nix-shell\n"
"these 2 derivations will be built:\n"
"  /nix/store/5yvz7zf8yzck6r9z4f1br9sh71vqkimk-builder.pl.drv\n"
"  /nix/store/aihgjkf856dbpjjqalgrdmxyyd8a5j2m-python3-3.9.13-env.drv\n"
"these 93 paths will be fetched (109.50 MiB download, 468.52 MiB unpacked):\n"
"  /nix/store/0xxjx37fcy2nl3yz6igmv4mag2a7giq6-glibc-2.33-123\n"
"  /nix/store/138azk9hs5a2yp3zzx6iy1vdwi9q26wv-hook\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"[nix-shell:~]$\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:69
msgid "Start the web application within this shell environment:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:71
msgid ""
"[nix-shell:~]$ python ./myapp.py\n"
" * Serving Flask app 'myapp'\n"
" * Debug mode: off\n"
"WARNING: This is a development server. Do not use it in a production "
"deployment. Use a production WSGI server instead.\n"
" * Running on all addresses (0.0.0.0)\n"
" * Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000\n"
" * Running on http://192.168.1.100:5000\n"
"Press CTRL+C to quit\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:82
msgid "You now have a running Python web application. Try it out!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:85
msgid ""
"Open a new terminal to start another session of the shell environment and "
"follow the commands below:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:87
msgid ""
"$ nix-shell\n"
"\n"
"[nix-shell:~]$ curl 127.0.0.1:5000\n"
"{\"message\":\"Hello, Nix!\"}\n"
"\n"
"[nix-shell:~]$ curl 127.0.0.1:5000 | jq '.message'\n"
"  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  "
"Current\n"
"                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  "
"Speed\n"
"100    26  100    26    0     0  13785      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:-- "
"26000\n"
"\"Hello, Nix!\"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:100
msgid ""
"As demonstrated, you can use both `curl` and `jq` to test the running web "
"application without any manual installation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/recipes/python-environment.md:102
msgid ""
"You can commit the files we created to version control and share them with "
"other people. Others can now use the same shell environment as long as they "
"have [Nix installed](install-nix)."
msgstr ""

